  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK582">
<l>ellārkku mellā nikaḻpavai yeññāṉṟum </l>
<l>vallaṟital vēntaṉ ṟoḻil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is the duty of a king to know quickly (by a spy) what all happens, daily, amongst all men.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
